      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, dependable ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs reliably and is ready for your daily commute or weekend errands! You'll notice some visible wear on the exterior and interior that comes with a well-used car, but mechanically it holds its own. A fantastic option for budget-savvy buyers who want solid transportation without the premium price tag!",
