    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Project Car \u2014 Priced to Sell! \ud83d\udd27 If you're a hands-on enthusiast or just need an ultra-affordable set of wheels, this could be your opportunity! This vehicle is in poor condition and priced honestly to match \u2014 what you see is what you get, no hidden surprises. It shows significant wear both inside and out and will require attention and repairs to get it road-ready. Perfect for a DIY mechanic, a parts source, or someone with the skills to bring it back to life. Come take a look and see if it's the right project for you!",
