    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Reliable \u2014 A Great Car at a Great Price! \u2014 Looking for a dependable vehicle that won't let you down? This car is in good condition \u2014 it drives smoothly, runs reliably, and has been well cared for over the years. You'll find some normal signs of everyday use, as expected, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal or performance. Mechanically sound and ready to hit the road, this is a smart buy for anyone who wants quality without the premium price tag. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll love it!",
      "price": 36000.0,
